title: Watch Dogs MegaTextures Mod v.1.0 by TheWorse
description:
============================
Year: 2014 
Genre: Action, Adventure, Stealth 
Developer: Ubisoft Montreal, Ubisoft Romania, Ubisoft Reflections 
Publisher: Ubisoft Entertainment 
Platform: PC 

============================
Description:
MegaTextures Mod v.1.0 by TheWorse for Watch Dogs 
This mod opens the graphics settings, which was shown at E3 2012!

============================
Installation:
Folder GMT.KZ_TheWorse_Mod_v.1.0 without high-resolution textures. 
Folder GMT.KZ_TheWorse_Mod_v.1.0_Textures with high-resolution textures. 
1) Copy the contents of the folder GMT.KZ_TheWorse_Mod_v.1.0 (no texture) to the directory installed games folder data_win64 
For example G:  Games  WATCH_DOGS  data_win64 
2) Copy the contents of the folder GMT.KZ_TheWorse_Mod_v.1.0_Textures (textures) to the directory installed games folder data_win64 
For example G:  Games  WATCH_DOGS  data_win64 
3) Run the game and enjoy the super-graphics in the game, which was shown at E3 2012!
